    "name": "STTI Career API (Siap Frontend)",
    "_postman_id": "stti-career-id-ready",
    "description": "\n# Cara Pakai Koleksi (Postman) – Bahasa Indonesia\n\n1. Buka Postman → **Import** → pilih file ini.\n2. Buka tab **Variables**:\n   - `base_url` → `http://localhost:5000` (atau URL Railway kamu)\n   - `token` → kosong dulu.\n3. Jalankan **Auth → Login** → ambil `token` dari response → isi ke variable `token`.\n4. Semua request yang butuh auth akan otomatis menyertakan header `Authorization: Bearer {token}`.\n5. Untuk upload file, pilih **Body → form-data** dan isi file pada key yang diminta.\n\n_Diperbarui: 2025-09-19 02:10:51 WIB_\n",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "base_url",
      "value": "http://localhost:5000"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": ""
    }
  ],
